{
  "stem": "4919.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he got a citizen of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became a citizen of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then after the war we met with him, because he, too, used to live in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] OK this is-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that yes, what I want to say-- still want to say.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At this shtetl it was a Jewish religious life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Always, always was a Jewish religious life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everyone knows he is-- he is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He got to go at Saturday shabbat to the synagogue, Friday evening to the synagogue, and even in weekdays some of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at the holidays everyone goes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At the high holidays, pesach, everyone goes to the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my mother's side, two brothers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The older brother was David and the younger was Josef.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they both lived-- we lived together-- until, I believe, in 1929 David was taken to the service, to the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he settled first, he settled in the city of Kiev.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then Josef was taken to the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he, too, settled there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he, David, eventually he returned home-- Married and returned home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Josef, he used to live in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And David was killed by the Nazis in 1941.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Him and his family, his wife and two children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I estimate it at, about 500.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only a Jewish shtetl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all around have been villages with Ukrainian population.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was four, I didn't mention, when I was four I went to cheder where the education was only in-- in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then until nine [INAUDIBLE] I stayed there until nine.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
